<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克吃惊地盯着女人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您丈夫是食人魔？”他问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个……偷金子的邪恶食人魔吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他喜欢偷金子和宝物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你知道他最喜欢吃什么吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克摇了摇头：“不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是面包！上面放着烤男孩儿的面包！”女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须马上离开这里！”女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我丈夫现在出去打猎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上就要回来了！他会吃掉你的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克知道他应该马上离开这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈给他讲过邪恶食人魔的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔喜欢偷金子和宝物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没想到......食人魔还喜欢吃男孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，杰克的肚子饿得咕咕叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的腿也开始发软。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克又摸了摸肚子：“求您了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他吃掉我以前，我可能会先饿死的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>求您了！给我一些吃的吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这不是一个好主意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会快点儿吃完离开的！”杰克恳求道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证！”他在胸前画了个十字，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求您了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人盯着杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，她重重地叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195136</EndMilliseconds>
